{
  "stem": "1736.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no contact whilst I-- we were traveling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, of course not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once you settled in to Mishmar Hasharon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a facility of writing letters through the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was contacted then by my father-- who I'm not sure whether he was in Australia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he was in Australia already then-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who had been told by my mother where I was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] aiming to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I wrote to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm not quite sure whether she already-- she knew that I had arrived or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got a letter from him, because I had the uncles there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would tell him that I was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that contact was really done sort of through-- through my mother, who was still in Aken Elbe until 19-- well, this was 1942.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have a letter here that was the last letter that was sent to her at her then known address.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It came back with a stamp over it to say address unknown or undeliverable, couldn't be delivered, where the postman had actually written [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in pencil on it, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll say it in English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN], which means sent to the, I guess, it's concentration camp in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the last we heard of her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think it was a letter sent by my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've got it here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I also got my letters back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I mean, I have a few of them, so I've just sort of picked out the one of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, that's the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I then lived-- we stayed in-- in- in Israel, in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
